'''史考特·白歐'''（'''Scott Baio'''，{{bd|1960年|9月22日}}）是[[美國|美國]]的一位演員和電視導演，出生在紐約<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20061439,00.html |title=Scott Baio the Man Who Can't Commit |work=[[People_(magazine)|People]] |date=July 23, 2007 |last=Jones |first=Oliver |volume=68 |issue=4 |accessdate=December 4, 2013 |journal= |archive-date=2016-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160416160519/http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20061439,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他最著名的角色是在情境喜劇《[[欢乐时光_(电视剧)|歡樂時光]]》（Happy Days）中飾演Chachi Arcola。自此之後他也在眾多電視節目中擔任客串來賓，並且也出演過一些獨立電影。他是一位註冊共和黨員並認為自己是一位保守主義者<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.buzzfeed.com/mjs538/40-celebrities-who-are-republicans |title=40 Celebrities Who Are Republicans |publisher=[[Buzzfeed.com|Buzzfeed.com]] |date=November 2, 2010 |accessdate=June 1, 2012 |archive-date=2017-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112014519/https://www.buzzfeed.com/mjs538/40-celebrities-who-are-republicans |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

